      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/641184502_18192847993351251_3733317974650974046_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s480x480_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgzODgzODk2MTkzNDAxMDc4Nw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjcyMHg5NjAuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=MowsLJBpdY4Q7kNvwEiIf8L&amp;_nc_oc=AdqLPyPKX8WODX3QjvGfnru9y7OwmTeWh_r2z7W3b9C9uvWVinRASRiqqfAyhyj1c6Q&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=weleW9QFjdx1xvcF6Qjirw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwjPMGbu5SZF-aAk0XOQDNk_6UarbkFj4ZYKkkFQ0a9GA&amp;oe=69CA2070" alt="Slide 1 fra @yogabybella" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/638860150_18192848110351251_8435722391398478263_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s480x480_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgzODgzOTAwMDg0MDM5OTEzNA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjcyMHg5NjAuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=_4xPnQT3VmYQ7kNvwGkdIeZ&amp;_nc_oc=AdocMU-si27MyuNdzQkt6nkHAitJkaRnclupLcH4JUKg1E5ULt7y7cwbAj5rkNduwAk&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=weleW9QFjdx1xvcF6Qjirw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyvU5erjrqwVi7Bw_qDVcYioOfV7MRDPRGlUTUkGi72KA&amp;oe=69CA2972" alt="Slide 2 fra @yogabybella" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/637694582_18192848071351251_8398062873188013018_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s480x480_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=106&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgzODgzOTEyOTYzMDY2MDI3MQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjcyMHg5NjAuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=kFdi-Eay1MMQ7kNvwFhr7sE&amp;_nc_oc=AdpT-GdZi_Ejiv54Tu6W_v3LNnRPcsqiy4PbhSyd52oKX3CUQ9khKhyIpPcZo9AqNcM&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=weleW9QFjdx1xvcF6Qjirw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afyj_1LS3GXd8mo1PjR3vt90zJwTdUAkcETsdivk8xA3jw&amp;oe=69CA1806" alt="Slide 3 fra @yogabybella" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/637704318_18192847951351251_7090192445538204455_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgzODgzODk5OTE3OTQzMTYyMA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkyMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=gyu_0bz67bYQ7kNvwFA2LPp&amp;_nc_oc=Ado1I8H47Hk_ZrsQOC_nQvcoIJouI1GI4A2wkiHTDXMKTcmI3HnSTBDfHaFXoPGDzk8&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=weleW9QFjdx1xvcF6Qjirw&amp;_nc_ss=7a3ba&amp;oh=00_AfwWricezqGKE08pVr12Qt2en7Byffe1cD5EtWi57SDEig&amp;oe=69CA350C" alt="Slide 4 fra @yogabybella" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (14 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@yogabybella</strong></p><p>I’ve been taking a quieter season after a very full year of teaching, retreats, and corporate work.<br/>
<br/>
There’s a kind of momentum that can build when things are going well - more opportunities, more ideas, more output. And yet I found myself wanting to slow down, not speed up.<br/>
<br/>
Yoga, after all, is more interested in depth than momentum. We know the practice extends beyond the mat and into how we shape our lives.<br/>
<br/>
It feels grounding to be back in my hometown for a while - slowing down and letting everything gently land within the familiarity of Australia.<br/>
<br/>
There’s more to share for 2026, but it will come slowly.<br/>
<br/>
For now, here’s some of the nature that’s been nourishing me.</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DVGTD2aATiL/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
